"{prog} will only download packages, install gpg keys, and check the "
"transaction."
msgstr "{prog} ຈະດາວໂຫຼດສະເພາະແພັກເກດ, ຕິດຕັ້ງກະແຈ gpg, ແລະ ກວດສອບທຸລະກຳເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:230
msgid "Persistent transactions aren't supported on bootc systems."
msgstr "ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບທຸລະກຳແບບຄົງຄ້າງໃນລະບົບ bootc."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:231 dnf/cli/cli.py:242 dnf/cli/cli.py:278
msgid "Operation aborted."
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກການເຮັດວຽກ."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:239
msgid ""
"This bootc system is configured to be read-only. Pass --transient to perform "
"this transaction in a transient overlay which will reset when the system "
"reboots."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບ bootc ນີ້ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ --transient ເພື່ອດຳເນີນທຸລະກຳນີ້ໃນ overlay "
"ຊົ່ວຄາວ ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກຣີເຊັດເມື່ອລະບົບເລີ່ມໃໝ່."

#. Only tell the user about the transient overlay if
#. it's not already in place
#: dnf/cli/cli.py:247
msgid ""
"A transient overlay will be created on /usr that will be discarded on "
"reboot. Keep in mind that changes to /etc and /var will still persist, and "
"packages commonly modify these directories."
msgstr ""
"overlay ຊົ່ວຄາວຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນ /usr ແລະ ຈະຖືກລຶບຖິ້ມເມື່ອເລີ່ມລະບົບໃໝ່. ໃຫ້ຈື່ໄວ້ວ່າການປ່ຽນແປງໃນ /"
"etc ແລະ /var ຈະຍັງຄົງຢູ່, ແລະ ປົກກະຕິແລ້ວແພັກເກດຈະແກ້ໄຂໄດເຣັກທໍຣີເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:260
msgid ""
"This operation would modify the following paths, possibly introducing "
"inconsistencies when the transient overlay on /usr is discarded. See the "
"usr_drift_protected_paths configuration option for more information."
msgstr ""
"ການເຮັດວຽກນີ້ຈະແກ້ໄຂເສັ້ນທາງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້, ເຊິ່ງອາດເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຄວາມບໍ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັນເມື່ອ overlay ຊົ່ວຄາວໃນ /"
"usr ຖືກລຶບຖິ້ມ. ເບິ່ງຕົວເລືອກການຕັ້ງຄ່າ usr_drift_protected_paths ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:267
msgid ""
"Operation aborted. Pass --setopt=usr_drift_protected_paths= to disable this "
"check and proceed anyway."
msgstr ""
"ຍົກເລີກການເຮັດວຽກ. ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ --setopt=usr_drift_protected_paths= ເພື່ອປິດການກວດສອບນີ້ ແລະ "
"ດຳເນີນການຕໍ່."

#: dnf/cli/cli.py:272
msgid "Transient transactions are only supported on bootc systems."
msgstr "ທຸລະກຳຊົ່ວຄາວ (Transient) ຮອງຮັບສະເພາະໃນລະບົບ bootc ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

